{"tid":317342,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［DSE放榜］讀緊樹仁輔心 你問我答","createTime":"2017-07-11T11:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T14:09:36.000Z","uid":128022,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d04a0ee739c42fb9f9ccdbb7ee7e8cb006aaf37d","tid":317342,"uid":128022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:26:18.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n我係香港樹仁大學輔心系既學生&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日就係放榜日<br />\n對心理學有興趣嘅巴打絲打可以留意返，樹仁輔導及心理學系可能會係你一條出路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n輔心系提供兩個課程&nbsp;<br />\n－輔導及心理學（榮譽）社會科學學士(輔心)，每年收生約110名<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n－心理學（榮譽）社會科學學士(純心)課程，每年收生約40名&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n前者著重培育心理及輔導專才，重視心理學理論及輔導技巧的最新發展；後者則著重令學員建立心理學專業和研究所必需具備的核心能力&nbsp;。<br />\n<br />\n輔導及心理學系(包括輔心及純心)是少數在樹仁不用修普通話的學系，&nbsp;<br />\n另一方面，輔心的學生要在YEAR 3完結前完成一共100小時的義工服務加50小時的訓練，而純心的學生則不需要。<br />\n<br />\n樹仁雖然比唔上八大，但佢係一個jupas以外嘅好選擇，有好多好有心嘅 Professor同埋好照顧 freshman嘅師兄姐添。<br />\n大家DSE有33222就可以喺7月12號至22號帶同近照、身份證正副本、學歷證明同200蚊去樹仁報名、仲會即埸interview即日俾埋結果。<br />\n<br />\n雖然樹仁呢一兩年發生好多事，但係其實對於唔夠分入八大心理學嘅同學都係一個選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有問題歡迎喺下面問，你問我答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e6e98de5001bb6af5ebb27aac0702e9a054174","tid":317342,"uid":128022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:35:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68c17de50d476e80ed80818bb7f0f2e56492f7db","tid":317342,"uid":128022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a605e36a3d08269b3b1fa1b99e316c51af5db035","tid":317342,"uid":128022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f586e2dbb8beab04e050289a4323abcee4734c3f","tid":317342,"uid":128022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:45:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45a7af22dacd5507295a6c6a0c2a2059a176fab4","tid":317342,"uid":128022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T11:50:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1e94b479928a66c78ddd926b751a2ff4d2018948","tid":317342,"uid":8296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"呢到學術台 返校園台開po啦清"},{"pid":"503c7c8650d722860ea5c34fc6634f2e6d4efcbc","tid":317342,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:59:23.000Z","msg":"樹中仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬有無試過比8大仔指住嚟恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b97fe5ed9599ec96d01cc389d9a347b5b62ef47","tid":317342,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"放榜先開啦，依家開只會被人踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}